            <h1> Basic Facts </h1>
            <p> Name: San Antonio Central Library </p>
            <p> Location: 600 Soledad Street, San Antonio, Texas </p>
            <p> Principal architect: Ricardo Legorreta, Mexico City; Johnson-Dempsey & Associates; and Sprinkles Robey </p>
            <p> Design Selected in 1991 </p>
            <p> Constructed in 1995 </p>
            <p> 238,000 square feet </p>
            <p> Capacity for 750,000 items </p>
            <p> Initial Construction Cost Approximately $38 million </p>

          </div>
