                <p>
                  The chief issue is that the building does not appear to work with nature. The bright red color, still luminous after years of fading, the perfectly straight lines,  the perfect spheres: nature provides no close analogs on earth. The building seems like a plastic juxtaposition to the trees in the foreground.
                </p>
